Sales_Data_Ecommerce
This dataset contains 160,000 records of user interaction events on an e-commerce platform throughout October 2019. 
It captures each user's browsing and purchasing behaviour across Browser and App channels, including product details such as category, brand and price, 
along with the user's location (US State) and an engagement score. It serves as the primary dataset for analysing sales trends, traffic patterns, and customer behaviour.

Promotions
This dataset contains 61 records of promotional campaigns run during October 2019. 
Each entry links a unique promotion ID to a specific product, the date the promotion was active,
and the discount percentage offered. It is used alongside the sales data to evaluate the effectiveness 
of promotions on purchasing decisions and overall revenue.AskSonnet 4.6
